  "texts": [
    "After passing the self-attention layer, the data is reduced by simply averaging along the sequence axis.",
    "The output of the convolutional backbone for every input spectrum is reduced to the size 64 by a single fully connected layer and is passed to a scaled dotproduct attention 18 with a single head.",
    "The output of the attention layer is averaged and directly connected to the last fully-connected layer, which outputs logits (i.e. predictions).",
    "The list of collected spectra is in Suppl.",
    "Table 6 and available from ref. 70."
  ],
